name: Falling Through Eternity Blue Twist
description: Falling Through Eternity is an audiovisual NFT collaboration between Rashid Ajami & Walter Krudop The falling man is in limbo, suspended in time. There is no past or future, only this moment where his limbs move like a mechanical puppet. We are all caught in this eternal grid lock and yet there is a beauty to this dance-like repetition. The NFT includes unique music and visuals.
